graph.data: ['L. A. Adamic and N. Glance, "The political blogosphere and the 2004 U.S. election: divided they blog." Proc. 3rd Internat. Workshop on Link Discovery (LinkKDD), 36-43 (2005)., http://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=1134277']
A directed network of hyperlinks among a large set of U.S. political weblogs from before the 2004 election. Includes blog political affiliation as metadata.
